This license governs the use of the Simjot Cryptographic Engine ("the Software"),
which includes all source code, documentation, file formats, and specifications
contained within the `main.core.security.crypto` package and its subpackages.

The Software implements proprietary encryption technology exclusively designed
for use within the Simjot journaling application. This license permits inspection
and study of the source code while prohibiting incorporation into other projects.

