       - CryptoConfig.java and all configuration classes
       - CryptoHeader.java and the proprietary .sjcrypt file format
       - CryptoException.java and all error handling classes
       - ContentType.java and all supporting enumerations
       - Any documentation, comments, or specifications within these files

   1.2 "Simjot Application" refers to the Simjot journaling software and any
       official derivatives, updates, or versions thereof.

